body_html: Which official site do you mean? I'm pretty sure the pre-installed nvidia packages (nvida-cuda-dev, etc.) should be in sync with the toolkit, which is all v9.1.85. Toolkit 9.2 is apparently not yet supported for Ubuntu 18.10.
